; Test.mmp - Jump test
; ===== Entry =====

; If this instruction is commented out, DispA should
; show 2, then 3. Otherwise, DispA should just show 3.
&Display3 Step

@ Display2
    &2 DispA
    
@ Display3
    &3 DispA


